name: Lisa Cano Burkhead
tweet: I’ve seen what happens when REAL leaders make education a priority.  Gov. @SteveSisolak raised teacher pay, put dollars into the classroom and brought accountability back to our schools!   That’s the Nevada we’ll continue to build.

name: Lisa Cano Burkhead
tweet: Thank you Chief Justice and thank you Governor @SteveSisolak.   This is the honor of my life. Now let’s get to work.  https://t.co/eM6Ny7Jpkz

name: Lisa Cano Burkhead
tweet: I’m a mom, wife and educator who was born and raised in Nevada.  And now, it’s the honor of a lifetime to be selected as Nevada’s Lt. Governor.  Together, with Gov. @SteveSisolak, we're putting Nevada families first and turning hard work into opportunity.  https://t.co/xK3QnSVuee
